{"tid":2283494,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"點解D巴士等燈位咁鍾意貼到前車咁埋？？","createTime":"2020-11-12T15:20:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-14T06:01:06.000Z","uid":117722,"like":22,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"7c70c68172eca5219d267b1f40710769fa15dc6a","tid":2283494,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"自己同前車永遠保持大半個車位距離<br />\nD仆街巴士佬就鍾意喺後面貼到你有咁埋得咁埋<br />\n你向前多少少避佢，佢就專登再向前迫返實你<br />\n萬一大串燒，前面又係電單車，就真係多得你唔少"},{"pid":"f6990f1877cb229f1f288fd5238f14b7e43d75b1","tid":2283494,"uid":190604,"like":16,"dislike":1,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:22:58.000Z","msg":"仲有啲大貨車<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />次次見到都好有壓迫感<br />\n上斜又貼到實一實 成日驚唔覺意溜後咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a05f758615930f8725d00f7bdaecd1088a2d248","tid":2283494,"uid":14073,"like":96,"dislike":1,"score":95,"quote":{"pid":"7c70c68172eca5219d267b1f40710769fa15dc6a","tid":2283494,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:20:56.000Z","msg":"自己同前車永遠保持大半個車位距離<br />\nD仆街巴士佬就鍾意喺後面貼到你有咁埋得咁埋<br />\n你向前多少少避佢，佢就專登再向前迫返實你<br />\n萬一大串燒，前面又係電單車，就真係多得你唔少"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:23:12.000Z","msg":"巴士無車頭又大部，你咪覺得貼<br />\n<br />\n一陣中間隔好多位你又話塞住條路<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8104d710fed576f925eb61b16273f569b4fac6d9","tid":2283494,"uid":194498,"like":29,"dislike":2,"score":27,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:26:42.000Z","msg":"不要活在自己既世界"},{"pid":"1af7d6820e6e16be8e84cf0a31f3bd73514fb955","tid":2283494,"uid":39990,"like":32,"dislike":1,"score":31,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-11-12T15:46:26.000Z","msg":"佢再留多幾個車位條路唔使用"},{"pid":"1358d16a7f27644a312e01c81bca1757862c0179","tid":2283494,"uid":44728,"like":23,"dislike":2,"score":21,"quote":{"pid":"7c70c68172eca5219d267b1f40710769fa15dc6a","tid":2283494,"uid":117722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-11